If not already in exploration phase, You must change the workflow to EXPLORATION phase.

{{#args.0.value}}
{{h2}}Change to the specified issue: `{{args.0.value}}`

{{h3}}Update Workflow
  1. Update workflow file `{{workflow.file}}`:
     - Set `Issue:` to `{{args.0.value}}`
{{#equals}}{{args.0.value}}{{workflow.issue}}
     - Keep the `Plan:` field unchanged
     - Keep the `Track:` field unchanged
{{/equals}}
{{#notequals}}{{args.0.value}}{{workflow.issue}}
     - Keep the `Plan:` field unchanged
     - Clear the `Track:` field (if present)
{{/notequals}}
     - Remove `{{args.0.value}}` from the queue if it exists
  2. Change current phase to exploration
  3. Send updated workflow file using {{tool_prefix}}send_file_content with path `{{workflow.file}}`

{{/args.0.value}}
{{^args.0.value}}
